{"body": "Could it be that AutosaveAssociation#save_has_one_association marks the foreign_key value into the parent object (to randax in the test case) when it should not do that (and keep the value nil).\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/rails/rails/blob/master/activerecord/lib/active_record/autosave_association.rb#L373\r\n\r\nThis causes the IdentityMap to load wrong object in Association#load_target:\r\n\r\n    @target = IdentityMap.get(association_class, owner[reflection.foreign_key])\r\n\r\n", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/1871966", "created_at": "2011-08-22T16:49:00Z", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/2628#issuecomment-1871966", "updated_at": "2011-08-22T16:49:00Z", "repo": "rails", "issue_id": 2628, "user": {"following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/martkaru/following{/other_user}", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/martkaru/events{/privacy}", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/martkaru/orgs", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/martkaru", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/martkaru/gists{/gist_id}", "html_url": "https://github.com/martkaru", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/martkaru/subscriptions", "avatar_url": "https://1.gravatar.com/avatar/2e348712cbd85915c66cadc462cae8b9?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2F262717604b93578b7309e4a57fe91447.png", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/martkaru/repos", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/martkaru/received_events", "gravatar_id": "2e348712cbd85915c66cadc462cae8b9", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/martkaru/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "login": "martkaru", "type": "User", "id": 25375, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/martkaru/followers"}, "owner": "rails", "_id": {"$oid": "523841debd3543c151010a6d"}, "id": 1871966, "issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/2628"}
